episodes.name: Bubble Trouble
episodes.overview: As the team relaunches their investigation on Skinwalker Ranch, they are surrounded by a shocking phenomenon.

episodes.name: The Drone Zone
episodes.overview: When the gigantic, invisible Bubble raises new questions for the team, possible answers suddenly fall from the sky.

episodes.name: Smoke It Out
episodes.overview: The team ignites a massive bonfire to investigate the Bubble. But what appears in the smoke is more chilling than anyone expected.

episodes.name: Bursting the Bubble
episodes.overview: As the team launches high-powered rockets into the sky on Skinwalker Ranch, they are frozen in shock by what they encounter.

episodes.name: Pushing Boundaries
episodes.overview: When the team deploys a cutting edge new technology on Skinwalker Ranch to study the mysterious Bubble, it leads to an unsettling revelation.

episodes.name: Posting Up
episodes.overview: As the team conducts an operation to mark the barrier of the massive Bubble anomaly, they make a series of shocking discoveries.

episodes.name: Lights Out
episodes.overview: After the team unearths new and bizarre clues from the Mesa on Skinwalker Ranch, a complex laser experiment leads to an encounter.

episodes.name: Swarm Weather
episodes.overview: When a stunning UAP appears above Skinwalker Walker Ranch during an experiment involving hundreds of illuminated drones, the timing of what happens next leaves the team in disbelief.

episodes.name: Darting Around
episodes.overview: When the team flies a cutting-edge radar device high above Skinwalker Ranch, it reveals shocking new clues about the Bubble and what may be inside the Mesa.

episodes.name: Hard Target
episodes.overview: While drilling in the Mesa on Skinwalker Ranch, the team makes a discovery that could literally be out of this world.

episodes.name: Hard to Handle
episodes.overview: After lab tests reveal stunning clues about the ceramic material, the team faces a hard decision about their investigation of the Mesa.

episodes.name: Hard Boiled
episodes.overview: As the team performs new scientific tests on the ceramic material found in the Mesa, they uncover evidence that something top secret may be buried on Skinwalker Ranch.

episodes.name: Fire in the Holes
episodes.overview: After obtaining shocking new data on the ceramics that came out of the Mesa, the team performs a final and explosively revealing experiment on the Bubble.

episodes.name: Meeting of the Minds
episodes.overview: After an explosive experiment aimed at the mysterious Bubble, the team examines the incredible phenomena they have discovered on Skinwalker Ranch with a number of world renown experts and scientists.
